text: Today and tomorrow,let each day grow and grow.
title: Black Hawk Down

text: Keep smiling and never give up,even when things get you down.
title: Black Hawk Down

text: ...tonight, tuck my children in bed warmly.
title: Black Hawk Down

text: Tell them I love them.Then hug them for me...
title: Black Hawk Down

text: ...and give them botha kiss good night for Daddy.
title: Black Hawk Down
